Arnold 4.1 Scene Graph Location Delegate Plug-ins
=================================================

Environment Variables
---------------------

ARNOLDTREE_4_1  The installation directory of Arnold 4.1
BOOST_HOME      The root of the boost directory.
KATANA_HOME     The Katana installation directory at compile-time
OPENEXR_HOME    The installation directory of openEXR

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/libarnold_ScenegraphLocationDelegatePlugins.so' to the
   'Libs' subdirectory within a Katana resources path.
